ConcurrentHashMap class

ConcurrentHashMap Internal Implementation

ConcurrentHashMap only locks portion of collection on update

ConcurrentHashMap is better than HashTable and synchronized Map as well

ConcurrentHashMap is fail safe does not throws ConcurrentModification Exception

null is not allowed as a key ot value in ConcurrentHashMap

Level of concurrently can be chosen by the programmer on a concurrentHashMap while initializing it

